        <article><![CDATA[<p><span style="color: #dd9122;"><strong>Required</strong></span></p>
<p><em>Activation of the Agent Chat plugin is required in order to access the configuration page for this task.</em></p>
<p>Set the criteria for assigning chats to agents that best fit your organization&#39;s needs. Consider criteria such as agents&#39; skills, availability, and the length of time since their last assigned a chat.</p>
